{"title":"雷锋叔叔青春永驻","authors":["祁辉"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":3,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋叔叔青春永驻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祁辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年都有“三·五”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但不是日期的重复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋的精神青春永驻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然是亲切的雷锋叔叔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋不老吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，雷锋不老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月只是剖面的年轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起来总是一棵常青的树！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋常在吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对，他无处不在——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶伤时他是万能的血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱天里他是回春之锄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年都有“三·五”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年年都有新的雷锋叔叔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管有浊浪，但清流不息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润着一个充满希望的民族！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}